{"tid":1612041,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武式抗爭，絕無意義，無謂犧牲。反正我們只知道，香港很繁榮，人人都愛國，祖國很偉大","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:33:52.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8d0ecc9ac48fc84bf6f8b30a4b6c193c1e7c38","tid":1612041,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"喜茶好飲，祖國繁榮，祖國偉大。<br />\n香港很繁榮，因有祖國支持。<br />\n<br />\n負面消息，示威遊行，勇武抗爭，烈士犧牲，警暴問題，警察開槍？我甚麼都不知道。反正偉大的政府把不良信息和負面消息都屏蔽了。<br />\n<br />\n我只知道天下很太平，喜茶好好飲，香港很繁榮，中國很繁榮，共產黨萬歲，熱烈祝賀新中國七十年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNiqsvc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNiqsvc.png&h=618595ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DahKH3O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDahKH3O.png&h=120828a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.baidu.com/sf/vsearch?pd=realtime&amp;word=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;tn=vsearch&amp;sa=vs_tab&amp;lid=9363898527253336865&amp;ms=1&amp;from=844b&amp;atn=index&amp;ssid=0&amp;from=844b&amp;uid=0&amp;pu=usm@10,sz@320_1001,ta@iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0&amp;bd_page_type=1&amp;baiduid=00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D&amp;tj=__0_10_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.baidu.com%2Fsf%2Fvsearch%3Fpd%3Drealtime%26word%3D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%26tn%3Dvsearch%26sa%3Dvs_tab%26lid%3D9363898527253336865%26ms%3D1%26from%3D844b%26atn%3Dindex%26ssid%3D0%26from%3D844b%26uid%3D0%26pu%3Dusm%4010%2Csz%40320_1001%2Cta%40iphone_2_9.0_24_77.0%26bd_page_type%3D1%26baiduid%3D00BEB0EB492147B819D91713BD0D022D%26tj%3D__0_10_4&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f15cb306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.baidu.com/sf/vsearch?pd=realtime&amp;word=%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&amp;tn=vsearch&amp;sa=vs_tab&amp;lid=9363898527253336865&amp;ms=1&amp;from=844b&amp;atn=index&amp;ssid=0&amp;from=844b&amp;uid=0&amp;pu=usm@10,sz@320_1